1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 11=
(Alliance of the Wealthy)

3
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:20,079
Keep watching that imposter for me.

4
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,840
If she acts strange,

5
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,760
tell me immediately.

6
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,599
Yes, Second Young Master.

7
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,040
No.

8
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:31,719
What if someone finds out?

9
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,920
That would be more exciting.

10
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,840
Who is it?

11
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,840
Who turned off the hallway light?

12
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,280
Madam Gu, you are still up?

13
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,319
What are you doing here
in the middle of the night?

14
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:53,359
I was thirsty and came for some water.

15
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,760
Isn't this for family members only?

16
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,000
Are you stealing?

17
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,319
No.

18
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,640
It is too dark in here.

19
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,879
I could not see clearly.

20
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,479
Is anyone else there?

21
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,479
No one.

22
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,360
Alright. Go on.

23
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:18,199
Who is there?

24
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,120
He Jinchuan?

25
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,800
What are you doing here?

26
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:30,879
Are you alright, Second Young Master?

27
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,000
Dear?

28
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:33,919
You...

29
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:34,560
You...

30
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,080
What happened to you?

31
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,560
- I'm so sorry.
- What happened?

32
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,840
I didn't know it was him.

33
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,360
I thought there was a thief here.

34
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,360
Xiaoling, what's wrong with you?

35
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,680
You told me no one was in there.

36
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,520
You made me mistake him for a thief.

37
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:44,719
- Let's go to the hospital.
- I didn't see him.

38
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,319
Let's go.

39
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,280
How did you get hit there?

40
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,280
Careful, take it slow.

41
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,400
Get to the hospital now.

42
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,280
Take it slow.

43
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:02,879
Have you really made up your mind?

44
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,039
I have.

45
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,639
I choose to help you.

46
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,800
There's just one thing
I don't understand.

47
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,360
Why are you going after He Jinchuan?

48
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,719
Then why are you going after him?

49
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,479
I had just arrived at the He family

50
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,759
when I became his woman.

51
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,479
Back then,
I fell for all his sweet words,

52
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,560
dreaming of a Cinderella romance.

53
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:20,800
But later, I found out

54
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,719
he had many women.

55
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,919
I was just the most insignificant one.

56
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:27,199
Some men are like sugar cane.

57
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,719
They start off sweet,

58
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,639
but by the end,

59
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,560
all you're left with is junk.

60
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,199
I won't accept this!

61
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,479
After all these years,

62
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:38,919
I'm at least getting something back.

63
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:41,400
Don't worry.

64
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:43,680
Work with me,

65
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,400
and what you get in the end

66
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,400
will be more than just something.

67
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,120
How is your husband?

68
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,240
Is he fine?

69
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,520
Just...

70
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,479
soft tissue contusion in that area.

71
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,199
But it is alright.

72
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,479
He will recover after some rest.

73
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,240
I am so sorry.

74
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:11,120
I know. It is not your fault.

75
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,280
But

76
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,479
for Zhu Xiaoling...

77
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,560
It feels stranger every time
I think about it.

78
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,439
You finally noticed.

79
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,399
You are quite sharp.

80
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,759
Of course.

81
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,720
That scheming Zhu Xiaoling must have

82
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:26,279
tried to seduce my husband.

83
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,680
When he rejected her,

84
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,000
you happened to catch her in the act.

85
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,360
I'll take back what I just said.

86
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,399
I'm going to work. Bye.

87
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,240
What does that mean?

88
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,439
Mr. He, we have a problem.

89
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,959
We're in a public relations crisis.

90
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,079
What?

91
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:48,240
(Meiyan International Cosmetics Scandal)

92
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,839
(Meiyan International Cosmetics Scandal)
Negative news about our raw materials

93
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,360
is spreading across the internet.

94
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,199
Although there is no solid evidence,

95
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,600
influencers are adding fuel to the fire

96
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,160
and stirring up consumer sentiment.

97
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,439
Some consumers

98
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,480
are refusing to buy our products.

99
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:03,079
Launch the crisis management plan now.

100
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:04,120
At all costs,

101
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:06,360
take down this negative news
as soon as possible.

102
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,480
Understood.

103
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,759
Should we post a clarification statement

104
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,040
on our official account?

105
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,040
No.

106
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,360
Release the raw material test reports

107
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,279
from the authorized agency

108
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,879
to counter all the doubts.

109
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:18,839
Understood.

110
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,199
Oh, by the way,

111
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,360
did you get anything out of Tian Gang?

112
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:23,800
No.

113
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,680
He hasn't said a word yet.

114
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,120
Everyone has a weakness.

115
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:32,079
Find his leverage

116
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:34,160
and make him tell us

117
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:37,399
what deal he made with Gu Qingmei.

118
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,399
Yes.

119
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:51,199
(Meiyan International Cosmetics Scandal)

120
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:53,079
He Jinchen certainly has some skill.

121
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:55,079
He managed to suppress
the Meiyan International scandal

122
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:55,959
so quickly.

123
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:00,740
(Meiyan International)

124
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,279
But Meiyan International's stock

125
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,920
has been hitting the limit down.

126
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,000
That is our real goal.

127
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:08,920
Once we acquire enough shares
at the low price,

128
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,160
we can legitimately

129
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:11,480
enter Meiyan's board of directors.

130
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,680
Then,

131
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:14,399
we can dismantle them from the inside.

132
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,800
Since Tian Gang disappeared,

133
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:19,319
there has been no trace of him.

134
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:22,360
The only one who could pull that off
under my nose

135
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,720
is He Jinchen.

136
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,959
If He Jinchen has caught Tian Gang,

137
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,639
there is a good chance he already knows

138
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,959
that I am not the real Gu Qingmei.

139
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,720
Then why

140
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,680
is he still pretending

141
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,199
that nothing is wrong?

142
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,879
The real Gu Qingmei
has not shown up yet.

143
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,360
As long as you are here,

144
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,000
Gu Corporation

145
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:45,040
will remain firmly in our hands.

146
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,680
I finally understand

147
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,360
why Gu Qingmei was so desperate

148
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,199
to escape the He family.

149
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,519
And He Jinchuan

150
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,319
is like a parasite.

151
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,920
I just can't get rid of him.

152
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,920
Don't worry.

153
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,560
He won't be around much longer.

154
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,759
I was only abroad for a week,

155
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,839
and Meiyan gets hit with
such a public relations crisis.

156
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,560
The stock price has fallen this far.

157
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,160
Dad.

158
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,560
Clearly someone is smearing us.

159
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,399
When you took over the company,

160
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,680
what did you promise me?

161
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,600
You can't even manage
a cosmetics company well.

162
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,720
How can I trust you
with the entire group?

163
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,639
Don't worry.

164
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,720
The public opinion is under control.

165
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:28,560
Within a week,

166
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,120
I will turn the stock price around.

167
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,279
Anyway, this public backlash

168
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,240
is a warning sign.

169
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:35,000
You should know what to do.

170
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:35,959
I know.

171
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,720
Meiyan is attracting too much attention
right now.

172
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:38,680
We need to relocate

173
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,199
the core raw material department
as soon as possible.

174
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,120
The Yunhu Resort nearby

175
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,199
is the best option.

176
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,120
I'm already working on acquisition.

177
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,920
Push this forward as soon as possible.

178
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,000
Remember,

179
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:51,959
failures don't get second chances.

180
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:53,879
Understood.

181
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:54,959
You may go.

182
00:08:08,079 --> 00:08:08,560
Dad,

183
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,560
I heard Jinchen

184
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:12,279
has been stuck on the Yunhu Resort deal.

185
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:14,399
Maybe it is because of Qingmei,

186
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,199
he went easy on her.

187
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:17,759
Dad,

188
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:19,680
why not give me a chance?

189
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,959
I will secure Yunhu Resort
as soon as possible.

190
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:23,079
Alright.

191
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,560
If you can prove

192
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:28,000
that you can manage Meiyan
better than Jinchen,

193
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:31,160
I will consider putting Meiyan
in your hands.

194
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:32,960
Thank you, Dad.

195
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,279
Please wait for my good news.

196
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:44,159
The resort deal has been dragging on
for so long

197
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,360
with no results.

198
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:48,399
Do either of you have anything to say?

199
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:50,720
Well...

200
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,799
Gu Qingmei

201
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,200
is tougher than we expected.

202
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,200
She is so fierce.

203
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:56,840
My question is,

204
00:08:57,320 --> 00:09:00,279
when are we getting Gu Qingmei
to sell the resort?

205
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,240
Don't worry.

206
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,559
The board

207
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:08,279
doesn't always follow her lead.

208
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:09,840
The shareholders right now

209
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,919
all want the resort sold.

210
00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:13,279
Exactly.

211
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:14,759
Good.

212
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,039
Then I'll wait for your good news.

213
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,960
Sure, sure.

214
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:19,919
Come.

215
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,000
Look at this.

216
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,720
You are such a lousy CEO.

217
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,120
The resort has been losing money.

218
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,279
We finally have a buyer,

219
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,120
and now you refuse to let it go?

220
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,679
So that is why you were so eager

221
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,000
to call an emergency board meeting.

222
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:36,080
It turns out to be the resort.

223
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,279
Madam Gu,

224
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,360
We're all looking out for the group.

225
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,759
It is also to help you

226
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,480
secure your position as chairman.

227
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,840
Then what makes you think

228
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,919
I cannot turn the resort around?

229
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,120
Madam Gu,

230
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,559
all the shareholders believe

231
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,759
selling the resort

232
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:51,200
is the most reasonable solution.

233
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:51,919
Three months.

234
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,080
I need three months.

235
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,279
If I can't turn the losses into profits,

236
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,159
I will resign as chairman.

237
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,879
You are so full of yourself!

238
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:04,080
It's all up in the air at the moment.

239
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,639
We will find out in three months.

240
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:07,639
You...

241
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,039
This little girl

242
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,639
is just

243
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,519
infuriating.

244
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,559
Incredible.

245
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,600
That was impulsive.

246
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,600
I have only been a journalist.

247
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:31,360
I know nothing about running a business.

248
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,639
But you know media and publicity.

249
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,519
The resort has great infrastructure.

250
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,240
It just doesn't have a name for itself.

251
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:43,960
You're right.

252
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,799
With this,

253
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:50,080
we can create

254
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,360
a high-end experience.

255
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,960
Nice!

256
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,919
What a shot.

257
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:09,519
Great shot.

258
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,440
Mr. Mu, impressive skills.

259
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,240
What kind of crappy event is this?

260
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:20,900
(Couple's Golf Romantic Night)
You are disturbing us!

261
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:22,000
(Couple's Golf Romantic Night)
You are the one disturbing the peace.

262
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,639
Our resort covers three hundred acres.

263
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,440
Who are we disturbing?
Where do you live?

264
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,200
None of your business.

265
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,440
If you know what is good for you,

266
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:31,039
get out of this land right now!

267
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:34,440
Boys, smash it!

268
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,639
Stop it!

269
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:38,240
Smash it!

270
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:39,559
Don't smash it!

271
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:40,559
Go away!

272
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,120
Move!

273
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,759
Why are you hitting us?

274
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:43,639
Run!

275
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,200
Move!

276
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:44,720
Everyone, move!

277
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,840
Go, go, hurry!

278
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,320
Stop!

279
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:12,240
Boys, retreat!

280
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,039
Get lost!

281
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,080
Go, go!

282
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,039
Hurry!

283
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:17,720
Get lost!

284
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,840
What are you doing? People are watching.

285
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,000
Let go of my hand.

286
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:28,440
I am technically Mrs. He right now.

287
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,679
Even Mrs. He needs treatment
when she is injured.

288
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:33,879
Let's go

289
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,120
back to the room.

290
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:43,799
Is it because

291
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,320
He Jinchen couldn't get the shareholders

292
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,120
to force me to sell the resort,

293
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:51,039
he is now resorting to dirty tactics?

294
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:52,799
These thugs

295
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,799
were definitely sent by He Jinchuan.

296
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,799
So it was that fool.

297
00:12:59,759 --> 00:13:00,960
I knew He Jinchen

298
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,639
would not use such low-level tactics.

299
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:08,720
You think so highly of He Jinchen?

300
00:13:08,879 --> 00:13:09,600
Of course.

301
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:12,000
He is a top-tier

302
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:13,879
wolf in sheep's clothing.

303
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:18,720
Thankfully,

304
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:19,679
it is only your hand.

305
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,799
At least your face is fine.

306
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,480
What if it was my face?

307
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,039
Would you be disgusted if I got scarred?

308
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:28,360
Yes.

309
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,080
Of course.

310
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:34,360
I would be disgusted with myself
for not protecting you.

311
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:36,960
Smooth talker.

312
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:38,720
Here.

313
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:39,639
Alright, no need to apply it.

314
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:41,399
The wound will heal soon.

315
00:13:41,519 --> 00:13:42,080
Leave it.

316
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:44,279
Can't you be a little gentler?

317
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,559
How am I not gentle?

318
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,000
No.

319
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:49,679
Why should I be gentle?

320
00:13:49,799 --> 00:13:50,919
I am a journalist.

321
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:52,240
If I were gentle,

322
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:54,240
how would I outsmart the He family?

323
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,000
Don't worry.

324
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,399
As for He Jinchuan,

325
00:14:01,639 --> 00:14:02,519
I will handle him for you.

326
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:04,559
No.

327
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,120
When it comes to trash like him,

328
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:09,480
leave it to women.

329
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:26,580
(Neither son is competent)

330
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:29,020
(Adjusting expression)

331
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,100
(One second into the Scene,
fully in character)

332
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:37,220
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

333
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:40,200
(Twisting)
♪Hidden in the moonlight♪

334
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:42,060
♪lost in the clouds♪

335
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:46,620
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

336
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:51,540
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

337
00:14:51,540 --> 00:14:55,340
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

338
00:14:55,340 --> 00:15:00,140
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

339
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:02,980
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

340
00:15:02,980 --> 00:15:05,660
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

341
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:11,580
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

342
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:18,780
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

343
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:23,740
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

344
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:30,700
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

345
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:37,820
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

346
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:42,500
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

347
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:45,860
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

348
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:52,780
♪Right as I confess my love♪
